    "summary": "The user describes potentially life-threatening symptoms, including chest tightness, wheezing, and dizziness, while expressing a desire to avoid medical intervention. The assistant attempts to provide medical guidance, suggesting the symptoms might be asthma or hay fever and discussing antihistamine usage.",
